{"priority": "major", "kind": "bug", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "drcsim", "full_name": "osrf/drcsim", "uuid": "{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/67/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/67.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/67/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/67/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/issues/67/incorrect-offset-for-imu"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/67/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "Benjamin Swilling", "uuid": "{da2df6bb-cc8f-4609-9cbc-b022925f975e}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bda2df6bb-cc8f-4609-9cbc-b022925f975e%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bda2df6bb-cc8f-4609-9cbc-b022925f975e%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/account/swillb/avatar/"}}, "nickname": "swillb", "type": "user", "account_id": null}, "title": "Incorrect offset for IMU", "component": null, "votes": 0, "watches": 2, "content": {"raw": "There's an incorrect RPY offset listed for the IMU attached to the pelvis.  I believe this is supposed to be a position offset instead.\r\n```\r\n  <joint name=\"imu_joint\" type=\"fixed\">\r\n    <parent link=\"pelvis\"/>\r\n    <child link=\"imu_link\"/>\r\n    <origin rpy=\"0.05991527603 0 -0.01415\" xyz=\"0 0 0\"/>\r\n  </joint>\r\n```\r\nshould probably be \r\n```\r\n  <joint name=\"imu_joint\" type=\"fixed\">\r\n    <parent link=\"pelvis\"/>\r\n    <child link=\"imu_link\"/>\r\n    <origin xyz=\"0.05991527603 0 -0.01415\" rpy=\"0 0 0\"/>\r\n  </joint>\r\n```", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>There's an incorrect RPY offset listed for the IMU attached to the pelvis.  I believe this is supposed to be a position offset instead.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;joint</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;imu_joint&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">type=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;fixed&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;parent</span> <span class=\"na\">link=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;pelvis&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;child</span> <span class=\"na\">link=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;imu_link&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;origin</span> <span class=\"na\">rpy=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0.05991527603 0 -0.01415&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">xyz=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0 0 0&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/joint&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>should probably be </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;joint</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;imu_joint&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">type=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;fixed&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;parent</span> <span class=\"na\">link=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;pelvis&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;child</span> <span class=\"na\">link=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;imu_link&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;origin</span> <span class=\"na\">xyz=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0.05991527603 0 -0.01415&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">rpy=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0 0 0&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/joint&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "John Hsu", "uuid": "{0a186eae-abf0-45